        "content": "<p>102. 試寫出一個遞迴函數找出一群整數的中位數median。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>int findMedium(int nums[]) {<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;int len = sizeof(nums) / sizeof(nums[0]);&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;//求出數列長度<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;int mid = 0;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;if (len == 1) {<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;return nums[0];&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;//若數列長度為1，則輸出該數字<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;std::sort(nums, nums + len);&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;//使用sort對數列進行排列</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;if (len % 2 == 0) {<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;mid = len / 2;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;return ((nums[len] + nums[len + 1]) / 2);&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;//若數列長度為偶數，則輸出中間兩位數字的平均數<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;}<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;else {<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;mid = len / 2 + 1;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;return nums[mid];&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;//若數列長度為奇數，則輸出中間位數<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;}<br />\r\n}</p>",
